2350.terms:
Who can take part?
•	The promotion is available for new and existing customers with registered Paddy Power accounts, aged 18 or over.

How and when can I qualify?
•	Applies to all ACCA or Bet Builder bets with 4 or more legs.
•	Applies to all markets and all sports except horse racing.
•	Does not apply to Enhanced Match Odds markets.
•	Applies to bet settled from 9th August 2022 to June 2023.

What can I win?
•	Money Back as a free bet if one leg of your 4 leg or more ACCA or Bet Builder lets you down.
•	Max Insurance free bet £/€10 per customer per day, referring to the day the qualifying bet is settled.
•	Free bet will be available for 7 days from when it is credited.
•	Free bet stake not included in any subsequent winnings.

When will I get my prize?
•	Free bets will be credited shortly after settlement.

What else do I need to know?
•	Applies to pre-match accumulators and Bet Builder bets only.
•	If any of the legs of your qualifying accumulator bet are postponed or abandoned, leaving you with less than four matches or legs, you will not be eligible for a refund in that accumulator bet.
•	Minimum odds per leg of 1/4 (1.25).
•	Bets that are cashed out do not qualify for the free bet refund.
•	Bets with the same selections and number of legs as the first qualifying bet will not count towards this offer.
•	Applies to all Online, Mobile, Phone and Text bets.
•	Offer does not apply to bets placed in retail shops.
•	Bets placed with free bets will not qualify for the offer.
•	Permutation bets do not count towards offer. Only bets placed on single line qualify.

Other boring but essential stuff
•	Paddy Power reserves the right, at its discretion, to exclude certain customers from this promotion and to change the terms or availability of this offer at any time.
•	Paddy Power rules apply.
•	If any term of the Offer is breached, or if there is evidence that a customer is abusing the Offer or using the Offer to guarantee profits regardless of the outcome (whether individually or as part of a group), Paddy Power reserves the right, in its absolute discretion, to reclaim the bonus element of such offer and/or void the Offer and any bet funded by the Offer and/or take any other action it deems necessary.
•	The full terms and conditions of Paddypower.com also apply to this offer.

SEO_FOOTER_TEMPLATE.text: If you have a hunch about the outcome of the fixture between Sacramento Kings and Dallas Mavericks, have a punt on it! We have odds on 67 different popular markets for Dallas Mavericks @ Sacramento Kings.

SEO_FOOTER_TEMPLATE.title: Where can I bet on Dallas Mavericks @ Sacramento Kings?
SEO_FOOTER_TEMPLATE.text: Bet on the Basketball fixture between Sacramento Kings and Dallas Mavericks, which starts on Saturday, 11 February, at 03:10.

SEO_FOOTER_TEMPLATE.title: How much could I win by betting on Dallas Mavericks @ Sacramento Kings?
SEO_FOOTER_TEMPLATE.text: If you bet £10 on Sacramento Kings to beat Dallas Mavericks at the current odds of 1.8, you would win £18. On the other hand, if you bet £10 on Dallas Mavericks to beat Sacramento Kings at the current odds of 2.0, you would win £20.

SEO_FOOTER_TEMPLATE.title: What are the other Dallas Mavericks @ Sacramento Kings betting markets?
SEO_FOOTER_TEMPLATE.text: You can bet on other NBA popular markets such as: Winning Margin (Bands), Double Result, Winning Margin (10 Pt), Tri-Bet, Wire To Wire. Also, you might want to check out these interesting online betting options: a £10 bet for Dallas Mavericks on Moneyline at odds of 2.0 would win you £20, a £10 bet for Dallas Mavericks 1 - 5 on Winning Margin (Bands) at odds of 5.0 would win you £50, a £10 bet for Dallas Mavericks / Dallas Mavericks on Double Result at odds of 2.8 would win you £28.
